query:
INSERT INTO dependence_chain(
                    dependence_chain_id,
                    status,
                    last_updated_at,
                    dependency_count,
                    dependents,
                    block_hash,
                    block_height,
                    schedule_lane
                ) VALUES (
                  $1, 'updated', $2::timestamp, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
                )
                ON CONFLICT (dependence_chain_id) DO UPDATE
                SET status = 'updated',
                    last_updated_at = CASE
                        WHEN dependence_chain.status = 'processed' THEN EXCLUDED.last_updated_at
                        ELSE dependence_chain.last_updated_at
                    END,
                    schedule_lane = GREATEST(
                        dependence_chain.schedule_lane,
                        EXCLUDED.schedule_lane
                    )
